## 🧪 테스트 케이스

### 1. 단순 연산
```
Input: 5;
AST: Literal(5)
```

### 2. 덧셈
```
Input: 2 + 3;
AST: Infix(Literal(2), Plus, Literal(3))
```

### 3. 우선순위 (곱셈 > 덧셈)
```
Input: 2 + 3 * 4;
AST: Infix(Literal(2), Plus, Infix(Literal(3), Multiply, Literal(4)))
평가: 2 + 12 = 14
```

### 4. 괄호
```
Input: (2 + 3) * 4;
AST: Infix(Infix(Literal(2), Plus, Literal(3)), Multiply, Literal(4))
평가: 5 * 4 = 20
```

### 5. 부호
```
Input: -5 + 3;
AST: Infix(Prefix(Minus, Literal(5)), Plus, Literal(3))
평가: -5 + 3 = -2
```

### 6. 여러 연산자
```
Input: 1 + 2 + 3;
AST: Infix(Infix(Literal(1), Plus, Literal(2)), Plus, Literal(3))
평가: (1 + 2) + 3 = 6
```

### 7. 복합 식
```
Input: 5 + 10 * 2;
AST: Infix(Literal(5), Plus, Infix(Literal(10), Multiply, Literal(2)))
평가: 5 + 20 = 25
```

### 8. 깊은 중첩
```
Input: 1 + 2 * 3 + 4 * 5;
AST: Infix(
  Infix(Literal(1), Plus, Infix(Literal(2), Multiply, Literal(3))),
  Plus,
  Infix(Literal(4), Multiply, Literal(5))
)
평가: (1 + 6) + 20 = 27
```

